'''''John na John''''' ni [[Gana|firime yo muri Gana]] igaragaramo inshuti ebyiri bombi bitwaga John. John umwe yashutse umugabo amugurisha zahabu mpimbano. Inshuti zombi zarimo zihunga n'amafaranga, ariko imodoka yabo yagenze nabi barara mu nzu y'abashyitsi. Igihe bakuraga amafaranga mu gikapu cyabo, yaguye hasi itera impungenge mu bashyitsi ndetse n'abakozi muri hoteri aho abantu bose bashakaga kwiba amafaranga     

Igishimishije, iyi filime niyo yagurishije cyane kurenza uko babikekaga, ariko yanze kwemerwa  muri Afrika yepfo  kuko hasohotse yo indi bisa yitwa Skeem yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Tim Greene mumwaka wa 2011. 

Muri 2017 abanyamakuru ba Ghanain begereye Greene kugira ngo barebe ibyo Asamoah avuga ko yahawe uruhushya rwo guhuza iyo filimi, ariko we akaba atari ayifite. Asamoah yemeye kugura uburenganzira bwo gusubiramo, ariko ntiyigeze akurikiza amasezerano. Nta kirego cyemewe n'amategeko, kubera ko ikiguzi cyo gukurikirana urubanza rw'umutungo bwite mu by'ubwenge kirega Asamoah kitari kuba ingirakamaro.

